    • Method Detail

      • createSearchInWorkbookIterator

        ISearchIterator createSearchInWorkbookIterator(ISearchParams searchParams)
        Searches all occurrences of a pattern in the workbook and returns the iterator. It's unsafe to modify the cells during iteration.

        To use the ISearchIterator replacement functionality the ISearchParams.SearchTarget is to be set to FORMULA.

        Parameters:
        searchParams - the search parameters
        Returns:
        the search iterator
        See Also:
        ISearchIterator.replace(String), ISearchIterator.replaceRemaining(String)

      • createSearchInWorkbookIterator

        ISearchIterator createSearchInWorkbookIterator(ISearchParams searchParams,
                                               int startWorksheetId,
                                               IRangeAddress startAddress)
        Searches all occurrences of a pattern in the workbook and returns the iterator. It's unsafe to modify the cells during iteration.

        To use the ISearchIterator replacement functionality the ISearchParams.SearchTarget is to be set to FORMULA.

        Parameters:
        searchParams - the search parameters
        startWorksheetId - the id of the worksheet where the search starts
        startAddress - the address where the search starts
        Returns:
        the search iterator
        See Also:
        ISearchIterator.replace(String), ISearchIterator.replaceRemaining(String)

      • createSearchInWorksheetIterator

        Parameters:
        searchParams - the search parameters
        worksheetId - the id of the worksheet
        Returns:
        the search iterator
